772
00:56:14.139 --> 00:56:16.528
Fuck. man! Fuck!

773
00:56:16.893 --> 00:56:20.351
Fuck! The only one that exists
is the one I confiscated?

774
00:56:20.472 --> 00:56:22.155
Yes.

775
