like that?

777
00:56:33.850 --> 00:56:34.607
He likes you.

778
00:56:34.824 --> 00:56:36.906
We are the same.

779
00:56:38.289 --> 00:56:41.770
We're not the same.
We're not the fuckin' same.

780
00:56:48.525 --> 00:56:53.679
