We get the fluid back from MNU.

781
00:56:55.587 --> 00:56:58.306
Yeah. and what then?
Then we both die. eh?

782
00:56:58.470 --> 00:57:01.223
Both of us dead.
That's a suicide mission. man.

783
00:57:01.352 --> 00:57:04.606
