906
01:07:26.266 --> 01:07:28.746
Fuck! Get out!
Don't fuckin' look at me!

907
01:07:28.892 --> 01:07:31.349
Get out!
Get the fuck out!

908
01:07:44.521 --> 01:07:47.137
Get out!
Everybody get the fuck out!

909
01:07:47.661 --> 01:07:49.982
