915
01:08:07.905 --> 01:08:09.987
These fuckers!

916
01:08:12.993 --> 01:08:14.881
Go. go. go...

917
01:08:16.738 --> 01:08:18.626
Clear.

918
01:08:24.610 --> 01:08:26.896
